  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large pan over medium heat and saute the onion until it is translucent.",
    "Add the garlic and ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the cumin seeds and coriander powder and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the lamb shoulder and cook until it is browned on all sides.",
    "Add the water and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer for 1.5 hours.",
    "Add the basmati rice and stir well.",
    "Cover the pan with a lid and cook for 20 minutes.",
    "Turn off the heat and let it rest for 10 minutes.",
    "Fluff the biryani with a fork and season with salt and black pepper.",
    "Serve hot in a bento box."
  ],
